milestones.description: Steven Taylor and Aaron Jones's 89-run partnership is USA's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 78 between Aaron Jones and Monank Patel
Aaron Jones has broken the record for most sixes (26) in ODIs for USA, going past Malhotra's 23
Netravalkar has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (42) for USA, going past Monank Patel
